{"title":"安装node npm nginx","uid":"210795c3b7447698486bb82bc6c0ddf8","slug":"linux安装node和npm","date":"2023-04-15T04:56:46.037Z","updated":"2023-04-16T08:20:29.642Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux安装node和npm.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","content":"<h2 id=\"linux安装node和npm\"><a href=\"#linux安装node和npm\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux安装node和npm\"></a>linux安装node和npm</h2><h5 id=\"1-打开linux的命令窗口，切换到-x2F-usr-x2F-local-x2F-目录\"><a href=\"#1-打开linux的命令窗口，切换到-x2F-usr-x2F-local-x2F-目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.打开linux的命令窗口，切换到&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;目录\"></a>1.打开linux的命令窗口，切换到&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;目录</h5><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /usr/local/<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"2-使用wget命令下载node包\"><a href=\"#2-使用wget命令下载node包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.使用wget命令下载node包\"></a>2.使用wget命令下载node包</h5><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">wget</span> https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/node/v16.14.0/node-v16.14.0-linux-x64.tar.xz<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"3-下载后解压安装包\"><a href=\"#3-下载后解压安装包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.下载后解压安装包\"></a>3.下载后解压安装包</h5><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">xz <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span> node-v16.14.0-linux-x64.tar.xz\n\n<span class=\"token function\">tar</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-vxf</span> node-v16.14.0-linux-x64.tar<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"4-找到并进入到node-v16-14-0-linux-x64-x2F-目录下的bin文件夹，查看node版本号\"><a href=\"#4-找到并进入到node-v16-14-0-linux-x64-x2F-目录下的bin文件夹，查看node版本号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.找到并进入到node-v16.14.0-linux-x64&#x2F;目录下的bin文件夹，查看node版本号\"></a>4.找到并进入到node-v16.14.0-linux-x64&#x2F;目录下的bin文件夹，查看node版本号</h5><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> node-v16.14.0-linux-x64/bin/\n\n./node <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><code>出现以下即初步完成</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">[root@VM-24-4-centos bin]# .&#x2F;node -v\n\nv16.14.0<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"5-添加软连接，先进入到根目录\"><a href=\"#5-添加软连接，先进入到根目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.添加软连接，先进入到根目录\"></a>5.添加软连接，先进入到根目录</h5><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /\n\n<span class=\"token function\">ln</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-s</span> /usr/local/node-v16.14.0-linux-x64/bin/node /usr/local/bin/node\n\n<span class=\"token function\">ln</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-s</span> /usr/local/node-v16.14.0-linux-x64/bin/npm /usr/local/bin/npm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"6-配置完成，查看版本号\"><a href=\"#6-配置完成，查看版本号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.配置完成，查看版本号\"></a>6.配置完成，查看版本号</h5><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">[root@VM-24-4-centos &#x2F;]# node -v\n\nv16.14.0\n\n[root@VM-24-4-centos &#x2F;]# npm -v\n\n8.3.1<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"linux安装nginx\